    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen retains its original factory finishes and boasts a flawless subframe, with rod bearing and VANOS services already completed for peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, riding on original suspension with no bushing fatigue. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical purity.",
