      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior is flawless, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks here. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the premium leather bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, the carpets are pristine under heavy-duty mats, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from the local dealership, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and a brand-new set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires. The engine bay is detailed to a high shine, and every electronic feature operates with precision. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a 'new car' experience in every sense.",
