      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been strictly maintained to factory tolerances. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, driving power to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is exceptional, with no subframe fatigue and all bushings retaining original elasticity for precise turn-in and dampening. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car exhibits zero paint oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear. It is a turn-key, mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
